        "summary": "## Decisions\n- Wiki should be local markdown files only, NOT on Mission Control server\n- Wiki location: ~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/\n- Wiki web interface running on port 8080\n- All 10 agents must log conversations to wiki every 30 min via cron jobs\n- Manual sync available on demand via \"sync everyone to the wiki\" command\n- Wiki server binds 0.0.0.0 for TailScale remote access (confirmed working)\n- **Broken**: wiki-sync-all.sh script returns \"0 new conversations\" for all agents despite having active Telegram sessions; root cause is `openclaw sessions list --agent` CLI command doesn't work as expected\n\n## Open TODOs\n- **[NOT STARTED]** Fix wiki-sync-all.sh or wiki-heartbeat.py to properly capture Telegram session conversations (script checks `openclaw sessions list --agent` which returns error or empty)\n- **[PENDING BOBBY ANSWER]** Bobby asked: \"Want me to set it up as a launch agent so it auto-starts and stays running?\" (wiki server stopping on Mac sleep)\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Every 30 min, all agents must log new conversations with timestamps to daily-logs\n- Manual sync trigger: \"sync everyone to the wiki\" or \"force sync all agents\"\n- Wiki server accessible via TailScale from iPhone at http://100.103.22.35:8080\n\n## Pending user asks\n- Bobby asked for wiki to be viewable on iPhone via TailScale — **DONE** (http://100.103.22.35:8080)\n- Bobby asked if wiki is up to date — **DONE** (manually synced current conversation)\n- **OPEN**: Fix sync script so it captures Telegram conversations properly\n- **OPEN**: Launch agent for wiki server auto-start (offered but not answered)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Wiki root: /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/\n- Daily log: /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/2026-05-03.md\n- Scripts:\n  - /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-logger.py\n  - /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py\n  - /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-server.cjs\n  - /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-sync-all.sh\n- Wiki server port: 8080\n- TailScale IP: 100.103.22.35 (device: bobbys-macbook-air-1)\n- Access URL: http://100.103.22.35:8080\n- Telegram chat ID: 8212808444\n- Current session key: agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444 (last message timestamp: 1777828076636, seq: 179)\n- Agent session keys: agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444, agent:emmy:telegram:direct:8212808444, agent:finn:telegram:direct:8212808444, agent:rex:telegram:direct:8212808444, agent:x:telegram:direct:8212808444, agent:yoyos:telegram:direct:8212808444, agent:cody:telegram:direct:8212808444, agent:dj:telegram:direct:8212808444, agent:reese:telegram:direct:8212808444, agent:tt:telegram:direct:8212808444\n- 10 agents: main, emmy, finn, rex, x, yoyos, cody, dj, reese, tt\n- All 10 cron job IDs (30-min wiki logging): 251fe123-5cb1-4389-96df-0be5a7a93165, 443695d7-719e-4ab3-8536-6b2d9a3dd37b, fc96aa3c-0bbc-43a4-84c4-7b00b0c46a7f, c7f39628-4f97-47bb-8ec4-70d200938690, 6878985b-3761-4ad2-aa88-18ec445421e7, d3ab0b21-9c58-4f65-9df8-a59de0937f29, fe9d977a-289a-4872-9c94-51bbf9d0739b, 750f75a2-47fc-4a2d-b986-9557c0ddd4ae, 473c6328-4063-457e-b666-f5e57d816e89, 9edad4c9-5742-48c0-8fd0-d948a1307b63\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Wiki server restarted on 0.0.0.0:8080, confirmed working via curl\n- [x] Bobby can access wiki at http://100.103.22.35:8080 from iPhone via TailScale\n- [x] Wiki sync checked — determined NOT up to date (last log 12:29 PM)\n- [x] wiki-sync-all.sh executed, returned \"0 new conversations\" (broken)\n- [x] sessions_history confirmed current session has uncaptured messages\n- [x] Manually logged current conversation to 2026-05-03.md (TailScale link setup, iPhone access, sync status)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Fix sync script to properly capture Telegram sessions (wiki-sync-all.sh returns 0 when it shouldn't)\n\n### Blocked\n- None\n\n## Next Steps