        "summary": "## Decisions\n- **Each agent owns their workspace**: Each agent (Dean, Emmy, Finn, Rex, Agent X, YoYo, Cody, DJ, Reese, TT) has their own folder at `~/agent-mission-control/team-spaces/{agent}/` and organizes it their own way based on their specialty — no imposed structure\n- **Wiki root is HOME**: WIKI_ROOT = process.env.HOME, with fallback to AMC_ROOT for files inside agent-mission-control\n- **Heartbeat protocol**: Every 30 minutes, agents log conversations AND review/clean/organize their workspace, update activity.md\n- **WIKI_ROOT changed from ~/agent-mission-control to ~/ (full home directory)**: Enables browsing all Mac folders (Desktop, Documents, Screenshots, etc.)\n- **Wiki now called \"Bobby's Brain\"**: Unlimited memory system for all agents\n\n## Open TODOs\n- **[IN PROGRESS]** Fix `renderFilesView` — view=files should show ~ (home dir), not default to scopeFolder='memory-wiki'\n- **[PENDING]** Rebuild wiki with simplified dashboard (Bobby wants more user-friendly design: \"Continue where you left off\" card, Who's Doing What, Quick Files, Recent Conversations)\n- **[PENDING]** Implement Mac OS default voice response for voice memos (after transcribing with whisper)\n- **[PENDING]** Bobby may want launch agent for wiki server auto-start (asked previously, never answered)\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Empty string `\"\"` in query params must be preserved (use `q.folder !== undefined ? q.folder : null` instead of `|| null`)\n- Files starting with `.` or named `node_modules` are filtered out of folder listings\n- Text viewable extensions: .md, .txt, .json, .js, .cjs, .ts, .py, .sh, .html, .css, .yml, .yaml, .toml, .env, .gitignore, .mdx, .log, .jsonl\n- Every 30 min, all agents log new conversations with AM/PM timestamps to daily-logs\n- Manual sync: \"sync everyone to the wiki\" or \"force sync all agents\"\n- Auto-tagging of conversations with topics (YouTube, Money, Emails, etc.)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- Bobby said \"When everyone gets back I wanna circle back to this message\" (clarifying workspace setup details) — resolved by him confirming agents choose their own structure\n- Bobby asked to see ALL folders visible (Desktop, Documents, Screenshots, etc.) — **IN PROGRESS** (file browser showing memory-wiki instead of ~/)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- **Wiki URL**: `http://100.103.22.35:8080`\n- **Wiki server**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-server.cjs`\n- **Team Spaces base**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/team-spaces/`\n- **Agent workspace folders**: deans, emmys, finns, rexs, xs, yoyos, codys, djs, reeses, tts\n- **Memory wiki root**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/`\n- **Heartbeat script**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py`\n- **Daily logs**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/2026-05-03.md`\n- **Wiki root**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/` (was ~/agent-mission-control, changed to full home dir)\n- **Wiki server port**: 8080\n- **TailScale IP**: 100.103.22.35\n- **Bobby's Telegram chat ID**: `8212808444`\n- **10 agents**: main/DEAN, emmy/EMMY, finn/FINN, rex/REX, x/AGENT X, yoyos/YOYOS, cody/CODY, dj/DJ, reese/REESE, tt/TT\n- **Cron job IDs**: 251fe123-5cb1-4389-96df-0be5a7a93165 (main), 443695d7-719e-4ab3-8536-6b2d9a3dd37b (emmy), fc96aa3c-0bbc-43a4-84c4-7b00b0c46a7f (finn), c7f39628-4f97-47bb-8ec4-70d200938690 (rex), 6878985b-3761-4ad2-aa88-18ec445421e7 (x), d3ab0b21-9c58-4f65-9df8-a59de0937f29 (yoyos), fe9d977a-289a-4872-9c94-51bbf9d0739b (cody), 750f75a2-47fc-4a2d-b986-9557c0ddd4ae (dj), 473c6328-4063-457e-b666-f5e57d816e89 (reese), 9edad4c9-5742-48c0-8fd0-d948a1307b63 (tt)\n- **Voice memos latest**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_254---01079fcb-5019-4e22-8324-fecd9ee56389.ogg` (transcribed: \"I'm not really seeing the files like I see them on my desktop...\"); `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_255---077e44dd-5d6e-44a2-83e3-d83f744594c8.ogg` (transcribed: \"Yeah, I want it to be for all of it\")\n- **Whisper path**: `/opt/homebrew/bin/whisper`\n- **Session keys**: `agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444`, `agent:main:subagent:{uuid}`\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Wiki heartbeat fixed to read session .jsonl files directly (captures Telegram conversations properly)\n- [x] All 10 agents synced with proper names (DEAN, EMMY, FINN, REX, AGENT X, YOYOS, CODY, DJ, REESE, TT)\n- [x] Time format changed from military (13:52) to AM/PM (1:52 PM) in daily logs\n- [x] Wiki renamed to \"Bobby's Brain\" — unlimited memory command center\n- [x] Team Spaces view and individual agent workspace views created\n- [x] All 10 agents notified and confirmed their workspaces via Telegram\n- [x] Empty string preservation fix: `q.folder !== undefined ? q.folder : null`\n- [x] WIKI_ROOT = process.env.HOME with AMC_ROOT and MEMORY_WIKI_ROOT constants properly separated\n- [x] TEAM_SPACES_ROOT constant added\n- [x] Dean organized own workspace with README.md including role, team structure, daily rhythm, active delegations\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Fix `renderFilesView`: change `scopeFolder = 'memory-wiki'` to `scopeFolder = ''` for view=files\n- [ ] Voice memo response with Mac OS default voice after transcription\n\n### Blocked\n- None\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **WIKI_ROOT = ~/ (HOME)**: Enables browsing all Mac folders, not just agent-mission-control\n- **memory-wiki paths hardcoded**: Daily logs, wiki pages, daily-logs correctly reference ~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/ regardless of WIKI_ROOT\n- **getFolderContents fallback**: Tries ~/folderPath first, falls back to ~/agent-mission-control/folderPath if not found\n- **Files view broken**: `scopeFolder='memory-wiki'` for view=files shows memory-wiki instead of ~/ — needs fix\n- **Bug confirmed**: `curl -s \"http://localhost:8080/?view=files\"` returns `📁 memory-wiki/` instead of `📁 /` (home directory)\n- **Root cause**: `renderFilesView` in view===files branch passes `scopeFolder = 'memory-wiki'`; should be `''`\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Fix `renderFilesView`: change `scopeFolder = 'memory-wiki'` to `scopeFolder = ''` for view=files\n2. Restart wiki server and verify home directory folders appear (Desktop, Documents, Screenshots, agent-mission-control, etc.)\n3. After fix confirmed, respond to latest voice memo via MP3 with Mac OS default voice\n4. Rebuild wiki with simplified dashboard design per Bobby's request\n5. Consider: should \"All Files\" show full recursive home browse or agent-mission-control only?\n\n## Critical Context\n- Wiki currently has too many tabs causing navigation confusion for Bobby\n- Bobby wants simpler navigation with dashboard-first approach\n- All agents confirmed their workspaces autonomously organized by specialty\n- Last voice memo transcripts indicate Bobby wants ALL folders visible, not just memory-wiki contents\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: I just asked Cody if he knew what the wiki was and he said he had no idea so please make sure that all agents know what this is and how to use it\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (sessions_spawn): {\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:aa6da0e3-d1f8-4d31-aeef-775ea03ca742\",\n  \"runId\": \"cf476e3b-c51e-4322-b4ee-4f19b34b36f6\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Track expected child session keys. If any required child completion has not arrived yet, call sessions_yield to end the turn and wait for completion events as user messages. Only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER...\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (message): {\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"messageId\": \"24614\",\n  \"chatId\": \"8212808444\"\n}\n- Assistant: **Done!** Just sent a broa