        "summary": "## Decisions\n- **Multi-word agent regex**: Changed `/^### ([A-Z]+) × Bobby/` to `/^### ([A-Z][A-Z ]+) × Bobby/` to match \"AGENT X\"\n- **Section collection**: Use flag `in_target_agent` to track when inside correct agent section, restart collection for each new section\n- **Speaker detection**: Only match `**NAME:**` if NAME is in KNOWN_SPEAKERS list to avoid false matches on bold text\n- **Message content**: Capture content after speaker label on same line using capture group\n- **WIKI_ROOT = ~/ (HOME)**: Enables browsing all Mac folders, not just agent-mission-control\n- **memory-wiki paths hardcoded**: Daily logs, wiki pages, daily-logs correctly reference ~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/ regardless of WIKI_ROOT\n- **AGENT_LOG_NAMES mapping**: Maps agent IDs (main→DEAN, x→AGENT X, etc.) for daily-log matching\n- **Most recent at top**: agent_lines array reversed before rendering so newest conversations appear first\n\n## Open TODOs\n- **[IN PROGRESS]** Investigate and fix YoYo Wiki Logging cron job timeout (150 sec timeout)\n- **[PENDING]** Confirm Bobby messages display correctly in transcripts after hard refresh\n- **[PENDING]** Fix `renderFilesView`: view=files should show ~/ (home dir), not scopeFolder='memory-wiki'\n- **[PENDING]** Address timestamp display (per-message timestamps not in current log format)\n- **[PENDING]** Rebuild wiki with simplified dashboard (Bobby wants more user-friendly design)\n- **[PENDING]** Skills tab in wiki home page showing which skills each agent has\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Provider config paths are protected (cannot use config.patch for models.providers.*.timeoutSeconds)\n- Agent defaults.timeoutSeconds already 1200 (20 min) - meets ≥10 min requirement\n- Cron-nested command lane timeout is 150 seconds (2.5 min)\n- Files starting with `.` or named `node_modules` are filtered out of folder listings\n- Text viewable extensions: .md, .txt, .json, .js, .cjs, .ts, .py, .sh, .html, .css, .yml, .yaml, .toml, .env, .gitignore, .mdx, .log, .jsonl\n- Empty string `\"\"` in query params must be preserved (use `q.folder !== undefined ? q.folder : null`)\n- Every 30 min, all agents log new conversations with AM/PM timestamps to daily-logs\n\n## Pending user asks\n- \"increase the models.providers.<id>.timeoutSeconds to 10 min if its less than 10 min\" — Blocked by protected paths; agents.defaults already 20 min\n- \"make sure that the correct agent files are with the correct agent tab\" — Done\n- \"the chat transcriptions should be clean and easy to read separated by a line and also telling me who is messaging like in telegram\" — Done\n- \"i only see the agents messages and not mine\" — Fixed in code\n- \"i should see the most recent convo at the top so I don't have to scroll\" — Done (sections reversed)\n- \"time stamps should be next to the messages\" — Per-message timestamps not in log format; session timestamp shown at section level\n- \"is everything ok?\" / \"you sent me a message saying the model timed out at 702pm\" — YoYo timeout investigation pending\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- **Wiki URL**: `http://100.103.22.35:8080`\n- **Wiki server**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-server.cjs`\n- **Wiki logs directory**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/`\n- **Daily logs file**: `2026-05-03.md` (9443 lines, 276KB)\n- **Wiki root**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/` (changed from ~/agent-mission-control)\n- **Server log**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/logs/wiki-server.log`\n- **Gateway error log**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/logs/gateway.err.log`\n- **Server port**: `8080`\n- **TailScale IP**: `100.103.22.35`\n- **Bobby's Telegram chat ID**: `8212808444`\n- **10 agents**: main/DEAN, emmy/EMMY, finn/FINN, rex/REX, x/AGENT X, yoyos/YOYOS, cody/CODY, dj/DJ, reese/REESE, tt/TT\n- **YoYo Wiki Logging cron job ID**: `d3ab0b21-9c58-4f65-9df8-a59de0937f29`\n- **Timeout error timestamp**: `2026-05-03T19:09:59.675-04:00`\n- **Timeout duration**: `150000ms` (150 seconds)\n- **Timeout lane**: `cron-nested`\n- **Session ID**: `session:agent:main:cron:d3ab0b21-9c58-4f65-9df8-a59de0937f29:run:e26636f3-b584-4e19-aa71-2d50ad58821c`\n- **Heartbeat script**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py`\n- **AGENT_LOG_NAMES mapping**: `{'main': 'DEAN', 'emmy': 'EMMY', 'finn': 'FINN', 'rex': 'REX', 'x': 'AGENT X', 'yoyos': 'YOYOS', 'cody': 'CODY', 'dj': 'DJ', 'reese': 'REESE', 'tt': 'TT'}`\n- **Known speakers list**: `['Bobby', 'DEAN', 'EMMY', 'FINN', 'REX', 'AGENT X', 'YOYOS', 'CODY', 'DJ', 'REESE', 'TT']`\n- **Voice memos latest**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_254---01079fcb-5019-4e22-8324-fecd9ee56389.ogg`, `/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_255---077e44dd-5d6e-44a2-83e3-d83f744594c8.ogg`\n- **Skills catalog wiki page**: `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/skills-catalog.md`\n- **Whisper path**: `/opt/homebrew/bin/whisper`\n- **Built-in skills path**: `/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/`\n- **Custom skills path**: `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n\n## Goal\n- Fix wiki so each agent tab shows ONLY that agent's conversations (not mixed content)\n- Clean up transcript display with speaker labels and proper formatting\n- Fix missing Bobby messages in transcripts\n- Investigate YoYo Wiki Logging cron job timeout at 7:09 PM (150 sec timeout)\n- Configure model provider timeoutSeconds to ≥10 minutes (blocked by protected paths)\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Most recent conversations must appear at top (scroll down = older)\n- Chat messages should be clean, separated by line, with speaker labels like Telegram\n- Bobby's messages must be visible alongside agent messages\n- Timestamps should be next to messages (not available at per-message level in current format)\n- Agent defaults.timeoutSeconds already at 1200 (20 min) - meets requirement\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Fixed wiki-server.cjs agent section filtering to collect ALL sections for each agent (not break at first non-match)\n- [x] Fixed speaker detection regex to only match known speakers (whitelist approach)\n- [x] Fixed regex to handle multi-word agent names like \"AGENT X\" using `[A-Z][A-Z ]+` pattern\n- [x] Fixed Bobby messages missing by capturing message content on same line as speaker label\n- [x] Fixed message div structure with proper opening/closing tags\n- [x] AGENT_LOG_NAMES mapping added to fix name mismatch (main→DEAN, x→AGENT X)\n- [x] agent-log view now collects ALL content from ALL agent sections in the file, then reverses\n- [x] Created skills-catalog.md with 55 built-in + 10 custom skills\n- [x] All 10 agents have SOUL-addition.md with workspace instructions\n- [x] All 10 agent SOUL.md files updated with workspace protocol section\n- [x] Wiki server restarted and running after all fixes\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] YoYo Wiki Logging cron job timeout investigation (last run failed >8 min ago at 7:09 PM)\n  - Error: `Command lane \"cron-nested\" task timed out after 150000ms`\n  - Need to check wiki-heartbeat.py for hanging or slow operations\n  - May need to increase cron-nested command lane timeout OR fix sync script\n\n### Blocked\n- Provider-level timeoutSeconds paths are protected by config system (`models.providers.*.timeoutSeconds`)\n- Agent defaults already set to 1200 seconds (20 min) - satisfies ≥10 min requirement\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **agent-log view bug**: Original code broke after first agent transition (DEAN→EMMY), missing second DEAN section at line 8026. Fixed by collecting all lines where not in a different agent's section, using header line tracking.\n- **Multi-word agent regex**: Changed `/^### ([A-Z]+) × Bobby/` to `/^### ([A-Z][A-Z ]+) × Bobby/` to match \"AGENT X\"\n- **Section collection**: Use flag `in_target_agent` to track when inside correct agent section, restart collection for each new section\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Check YoYo's wiki-heartbeat script for hanging or slow operations causing timeout\n2. Either fix YoYo sync script OR increase cron-nested command lane timeout\n3. Confirm Bobby sees his messages in transcripts after latest wiki-server.cjs fix\n4. Verify most recent conversations appear at top (06:03 PM should appear before 1:52 PM)\n5. Fix `renderFilesView` to show home directory instead of memory-wiki\n6. Consider adding Skills tab to wiki showing which skills each agent uses\n\n## Critical Context\n- Daily log 2026-05-03.md has multiple DEAN sections: line 3 (1:52 PM) and line 8026 (05:53 PM)\n- Dean is the main agent (id='main') but logged as 'DEAN' in daily logs\n- Agent X (id='x') logged as 'AGENT X' in daily logs\n- The wiki-server.cjs file was edited multiple times — needs verification the current logic is correct\n- getDailyLogsForAgent(agent) takes agent object or string id, maps to log name via AGENT_LOG_NAMES\n- Log file format: `### AGENT × Bobby` headers with `**Time:** HH:MM PM` per session block\n- Message format: `**SPEAKER:**` followed by content on same or subsequent lines\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n\n## Goal\nSet up the wiki server (Bobby's Brain) to auto-start on boot and run permanently as a LaunchAgent.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Wiki server must always stay running (persistent)\n- Server runs at ~/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-server.cjs\n- Logs go to ~/.openclaw/logs/wiki-server.log\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Restarted wiki server manually (running on port 8080)\n- [x] Verified server listening on all interfaces (0.0.0.0:8080)\n- [x] Verified TailScale connected with IP 100.103.22.35\n- [x] Created LaunchAgent plist at ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.bobby.wiki-server.plist\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Loading the LaunchAgent to enable auto-start\n- [ ] Verifying LaunchAgent is registered with launchd\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Create LaunchAgent instead of other options**: LaunchAgent is the standard macOS way to keep services running and auto-start on boot, which matches the user's requirement for the wiki to \"always be on\"\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Load the LaunchAgent: `launchctl load ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.bobby.wiki-server.plist`\n2. Verify it's registered: `launchctl list | grep wiki`\n3. Verify server responds after load\n\n## Critical Context\n- Server started manually shows: \"Bobby's Brain running at http://0.0.0.0:8080\"\n- Access via TailScale: http://100.103.22.35:8080\n- Deprecation warning about url.parse() in the server code (CVE-related but low risk)\n- Server PID: 58145\n- Only one device online via TailScale: 100.103.22.35 (bobbys-macbook-air-1)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Script: /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-server.cjs\n- Node binary: /opt/homebrew/bin/node\n- LaunchAgent plist: /Users/bobbygalletta/Library/LaunchAgents/com.bobby.wiki-server.plist\n- Log file: /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/logs/wiki-server.log\n- Server port: 8080\n- TailScale IP: 100.103.22.35\n- Server socket: IPv4 0x23f27fe5f70f238\n- LaunchAgent label: com.bobby.wiki-server\n- PID: 58145\n- Working directory: /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: [OpenClaw heartbeat poll]\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): {\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-05-03.md'\"\n}\n- Assistant: HEARTBEAT_OK\n[non-text content: thinking]\n- User: open the wiki on safari please\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (browser): {\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"browser\",\n  \"error\": \"INVALID_REQUEST: Error: Chrome MCP existing-session attach for profile \\\"user\\\" could not connect to Chrome. Enable remote debugging in the browser inspect page, keep the browser open, approve the attach prompt, and retry. If you do not need your signed-in browser session, use the managed \\\"openclaw\\\" profile instead. Last error: Could not connect to Chrome. Check if Chrome is running.\\nCause: Could not find DevToolsActivePort for chrome at /Users/bobbygalletta/Library/Application Support/Google/Chrome/DevToolsActivePort\"\n}\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): (no output)\n- Assistant: Done! Safari should have opened with the wiki at http://100.103.22.35:8080\n[non-text content: thinking]\n- User: it says the server is unable to connect. the wiki should always be on\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-05-03.md\n\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/Users/bobbygalletta/Library/LaunchAgents/com.bobby.wiki-server.plist\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/wiki/skills-catalog.md\n/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-server.cjs\n\n</modified-files>",
